11
00:02:35.738 --> 00:02:38.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Debe de estar enorme…

12
00:02:49.168 --> 00:02:50.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
